(56664, 'D798BE2B-30FF-4297-9A80-EEA5EDE7BD67', 'I woke up this morning thinking about you date with Ken tonight  feeling sad and hurt. If you want to have a romantic, non monogomous relationship with him, I’m fine with that. But while he is on your board and without the consent of his girlfriend/fiance, I’m not. These relationships hurt me. Going out on a date while things are so raw, almost exactly 2 years after you first told me, and between Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur hurts more and feels like a provocation. I do not want to end our marriage over your need to engage with men in unethical relationships. It has and will continue to hurt our marriage. The impact is that it makes me feel hurt, sad and disconnected from you.', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-09-29T06:59:05.596774'),
(56665, 'DE8A20E3-6CEA-4E11-AE5C-27989A42A66D', 'Thanks for sharing where you are love and your feelings. I️ am fully aware that you aren’t ok with my relationships in the way that they stand today. I️ don’t need you to clarify that anymore. In the same way that I️ don’t think I️ need to clarify why these relationships are what they are to me. I️’m having dinner tonight with Ken. I️ need to talk to him about everything that is going on. The rules changed for you but I️ never got to discuss them with him or anyone else I️’m connected to. I️ haven’t seen Ken one on one since the early part of the summer and probably won’t again for a few months. It just happens to be the night he is free and not traveling. I️’m not trying to provoke you in any way. But this is my truth just as much as it is yours. And this is the tension that now lives in our marriage. It makes me profoundly sad as well. I️ am going to spend time thinking and talking to him and my therapist about what I️ can do. But for now, I️ can just say I️’m really sorry this is hurting you. That’s not my goal and it hurts me to know you are hurting. I️ don’t want to lie to you - which would hurt in other ways. So I️ am being bare and vulnerable in sharing where I️ am today and hope you can accept me.', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-09-29T07:45:18.219849'),
