(56689, '195A0841-D1CC-4A91-B41F-DFCDF8A667E3', 'Love, I know that you are struggling. What you are doing at climb hire is incredible. You are changing so many lives. I know you have some really difficult conversations ahead of you today and difficult decisions to make. I am here for you. If there is anything I can do to support you…just ask. I love you dearly.', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2022-09-30T07:50:02.586162'),
(56690, '89BDBCA8-F4BF-4030-8C5A-50B2DF87CD46', 'Thanks my love. I️ really appreciate this note. I️ think the thing that would help me the most is to find places where we connect and are happy and try to focus there for a week or two. I️ think I️’m just breaking under the constant messages of what doesn’t work for you and us. I️ hope many things do work for us and that we can just try to find them and focus on them for a bit. I️ need some places to “win” these days because it just feels like everything is failing right now. I️ don’t want to hide or ignore your feelings. Or my own. But I can only take so much of the negativity before I️ collapse. It takes effort to see the good in us. A lot more effort than noticing the bad. So that’s my request for both of us - to look for the good and to build it proactively. ', 'Nitzan', 'David', '2022-09-30T09:04:29.791132'),
